# How to build a Foundation Model(LLMâ€™s)  on local machine without connecting to internet.
Download and Install OLLAMA on your Machine
Once installed, Open Terminal and run the OLLAMA to run any of the model, 

ollama run llama3.2 < - this will install and run the llama3, if already installed it will run

ollama run gemma2:2b


Install any of those models using ModelsLibrary 
